{"tid":520592,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"大家平時點玩Lego Game?","createTime":"2018-01-05T14:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T16:07:10.000Z","uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9260b356cdf7c63bae540a7f336311e4e0db94cc","tid":520592,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:59:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Glh8ytEl58g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGlh8ytEl58g&d=3G27iXfkleI%2BSqobtAB8jtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5c4aaf5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Glh8ytEl58g</a><br />\n<br />\nLego Game一向食古不化翻抄模式，大體上的玩法如下<br />\n<br />\n1.玩通故事模式，熟習遊戲技能能力<br />\n2.開始準備儲人仔，特別是敵人角色(例如玩Star Wars要特別著重Sith Lord同Bounty Hunter)<br />\n3.有曬所有人物能力就可以玩自由模式拿走所有隱藏物品<br />\n4.玩埋餘下的隱藏關去，隱藏關十分參差，有些很難有些很易，又或者單純惡搞，總之自己執生<br />\n5.做齊四個步驟如無意外就可以100.0%了<br />\n<br />\n定還是大家已經無咩耐性，玩通左故事模式當打爆機去，好似短片攻略咁？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d768e9c750fb45ff614bd59dd2243acc9761bf","tid":520592,"uid":48132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"我玩法就係一開波即刻入哂d secret code先<br />\n跟住通常就會有好多能力<br />\n又乘大點數又自動吸錢，gold brick探測果d<br />\n玩star wars係咁harry potter又係咁<br />\n理論上好快玩完<br />\n不過到依家都未試到玩gold brick隱藏關"},{"pid":"8a7f242c3d9bba6a6e3a79fbc67d5e18c1749694","tid":520592,"uid":59328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f4d768e9c750fb45ff614bd59dd2243acc9761bf","tid":520592,"uid":48132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"我玩法就係一開波即刻入哂d secret code先<br />\n跟住通常就會有好多能力<br />\n又乘大點數又自動吸錢，gold brick探測果d<br />\n玩star wars係咁harry potter又係咁<br />\n理論上好快玩完<br />\n不過到依家都未試到玩gold brick隱藏關"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"咁玩好無聊，我全能力都自己賺，不過第一cheat code一定係翻倍錢"},{"pid":"362206f0052fbf4f0821c5ea691d80c9105b2c65","tid":520592,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1